# Infrastructure & dev tools

- Secrets only via CI/Git OIDC or vault — not plaintext in terraform state without encryption design.
- Pin image digests or tags per policy; non-root containers; minimal attack surface.
- CI: fail on high CVE where policy says so; cache keys must be deterministic.
- Web3: RPC URLs and indexer endpoints are configuration, not repo secrets; document rotation.
- Use `devinfra-engineer` persona for platform changes.
